Jadarius M. WARDLOW, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4037 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. December 19, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:
